{"tid":1435332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪忘記咗，咁係時候同大家温下書","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:26:17.000Z","uid":255524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8eb405298d342cab1faf916083a40e81bd8e84","tid":1435332,"uid":255524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"温啲咩呢，就係<strong>示威囗號</strong><br />\n呢排我發現大家會叫嘅多數係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「香港人 加油」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「光復香港 時代革命」</span><br />\n好耐無聽過同五大訴求有關嘅口號<br />\n有嘅都只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「五大訴求 缺一不可」</span><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得6.12下午三點決定衝立法嗰時，大家一齊叫<strong>撤回 撤回 撤回</strong><br />\n仲有要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不撤不散</strong></span><br />\n嗰時大家同心一致，show畀外界睇我哋嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n仲有五大訴求的口號，好耐無聽過啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「反送中，抗惡法，撤回逃犯條例」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「追究警察濫權，成立獨立調查委員會」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「釋放被捕義士，撤回暴動定性」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「立即實行雙普選」</span><br />\n<br />\n好啦，陣間機場見"},{"pid":"c7a5eaead111d6302bf2a1eee94359bb748c234f","tid":1435332,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"香港警察係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐怖分子</span><br />\n無差別攻擊市民<br />\n<br />\n警方係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共恐怖組織</span><br />\n勾結黑社會<br />\n<br />\n跪求文宣組幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n唔好再侮辱狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c07e60ae54f118fcc752576b2e8abbaa8f05b9","tid":1435332,"uid":255524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a5eaead111d6302bf2a1eee94359bb748c234f","tid":1435332,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"香港警察係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐怖分子</span><br />\n無差別攻擊市民<br />\n<br />\n警方係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共恐怖組織</span><br />\n勾結黑社會<br />\n<br />\n